{"type": "article", "id": 13651, "title": "「 夏末单车」之骑车也可以打伞", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-18T08:03:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135742IgeQX4DjBrc57pLW.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自韩国的 KT Design 推出的这款雨伞本意是让“都市低头族”更加方便地使用手机，但是本着不应该纵容“低头族”的“顽固思想”，我们觉得用来骑车时候使用是个不错的选择。骑车打伞需要单手扶车把，容易带来危险。而如果将雨伞挂在手臂上，这样两只手就都可以用来扶稳车把了。这款设计曾获得 Red Dot Design Award 红点设计大奖，这是<a href=\"http://soho.olleh.com/ProductDtl.do?pcd=156\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141338JvMIlQVsu9DKb7Fo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141338U5QpMDb8u2yrAHiq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413393z6xb2rNhgVo4MEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141340fy50bF8i1GILCcnk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}